# Description : Rock Paper Scissors Game
####################################################
- Simple Rock Paper Scissors game implemented in Python.
- The game allows a player to choose between rock, paper, or scissors.
- The computer randomly selects one of the three options.
- The game determines the winner based on the standard rules:
  - Rock beats Scissors
  - Scissors beats Paper
  - Paper beats Rock
- The game announces the result of the match, indicating whether the player won, lost, or if it was a tie.
# To run the game, simply execute the script in a Python environment.
# The player will be prompted to enter their choice, and the game will display the outcome.